        <description>Casio's Knight Leon is a clone of Konami's &lt;a href="/search/quick?game=Knightmare"&gt;Knightmare&lt;/a&gt;. In this top-view game you control a brave and handsome knight, Leon, that has to shoot bullets at various types of enemies. Shooting a series of enemies can grant you invulnerability or a shield.
